        <!-- SEO内容区域 -->
        <section class="seo-content">
            <div class="seo-section" id="what-is">
                <h2>What Is AI Image Background Remover?</h2>
                <p>AI Image Background Remover is a free online tool that uses artificial intelligence to automatically remove backgrounds from images. Powered by TensorFlow.js and ONNX Runtime Web, the tool runs entirely in your browser, ensuring complete privacy—no images are uploaded to any server. It supports various image formats including JPG, PNG, and WebP, and offers multiple AI models for different needs: lightweight for speed, standard for accuracy, and human segmentation for portraits. Whether you're an e-commerce seller needing product photos on transparent backgrounds, a graphic designer creating composites, or a social media user making memes, this tool provides professional-quality results in seconds.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="seo-section" id="how-to-use">
                <h2>How to Use AI Image Background Remover</h2>
                <p>Using the AI Image Background Remover is simple: First, upload an image by dragging and dropping it onto the upload area or clicking to select a file. The tool accepts images up to 10MB. Second, choose an AI model from the dropdown: Lightweight (U2NetP) for fast processing, Standard (U2Net) for higher accuracy, or Human Segmentation for portraits. Third, select a background option: transparent (default), white, black, or custom color. Fourth, click the 'Remove Background' button. The AI will process the image locally in your browser, showing a progress bar. Once done, you'll see side-by-side previews of the original and processed images. Finally, click 'Download PNG' to save the result. You can also 'Process Another' to start over.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="seo-section" id="about-us">
                <h2>About Us</h2>
                <p>BgRemover is part of a suite of free online tools built to empower creators with accessible AI technology. Our mission is to make advanced image editing capabilities available to everyone without cost or complexity. The tool leverages open-source projects like rembg-web and ONNX Runtime Web to deliver state-of-the-art background removal directly in the browser. We prioritize user privacy—all processing happens locally, and no data is stored. Our team consists of developers passionate about web performance and user experience. We continuously update the tool based on community feedback and technological advancements. Revenue from non-intrusive ads and optional donations helps cover hosting and development costs, keeping the tool free for all.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="seo-section" id="terms-of-use">
                <h2>Terms of Use</h2>
                <p>By using the AI Image Background Remover tool, you agree to these Terms of Use. The tool is provided for personal, non-commercial use only. You must not use it for illegal purposes, including copyright infringement, harassment, or creating deceptive content. All processed images remain your property; however, you are responsible for ensuring you have the right to edit and distribute them. The tool is not affiliated with any third-party services except those explicitly mentioned. We reserve the right to modify or discontinue the tool at any time. We are not liable for any damages arising from use of the tool. Third-party links may appear; we are not responsible for their content. If you disagree with these terms, discontinue use immediately.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="seo-section" id="privacy-policy">
                <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
                <p>Your privacy is paramount. The AI Image Background Remover processes images entirely client-side using JavaScript and WebAssembly; no image data is transmitted to our servers. We do not collect, store, or share any personal information. The tool may display advertisements via Google AdSense, which may use cookies for personalized ads; you can opt out through Google's Ads Settings. We use Google Analytics for anonymized usage statistics (e.g., page views, button clicks) to improve the tool; this data cannot identify individuals. The website uses SSL encryption for security. We do not sell or rent user data. This policy may be updated; continued use implies acceptance.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

